The paper also discusses the implementation of the proposed mechanism in a distributed manner, which is relevant to the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of numerical analysis and performance evaluation suggests relevance to the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia), while the discussion of fairness among links in the network suggests relevance to the sub-category cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
